snippet.title: Project Brutality - Doom Mod Madness
snippet.description:
Project Brutality brings you the best in excess! It takes everything that made Brutal Doom great and takes it even further, adding a dizzying array of options, weaponry, enemies and of course finishing moves into the mix. You could say it's a bit fun.

PROJECT BRUTALITY
http://www.moddb.com/mods/brutal-doom/addons/project-brutality

MAPS OF CHAOS
http://www.moddb.com/mods/brutal-doom/addons/brutalized-doom-and-doom-ii
